  "pageTitle": "Two product families for modern resource recovery",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"products-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Product Families</p>\n        <h1 id=\"products-title\">Two equipment platforms cover optical sorting and heavy-duty material recovery</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">Compare AI optical sorting systems for recyclable plastics and integrated C&D waste recycling lines for construction, decoration, demolition, and bulky waste projects.</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-family-intro\" id=\"product-comparison\" aria-labelledby=\"product-families-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Solution Paths</p>\n        <h2 id=\"product-families-title\">Product matching begins with material stream, site constraints, and output goals</h2>\n        <p>One product family is built for high-value plastic recognition and optical sorting. The other is built for heavy-duty crushing, screening, and resource utilization in C&D and bulky waste projects.</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/super-sorting.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN super optical sorting system configuration with modular sorting equipment\">\n          </picture>\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Super Optical Sorting System</p>\n            <h2 id=\"ai-family-title\">Optical sorting platform for recyclable plastics</h2>\n            <p>Modular sorting modules identify and separate PET bottles, HDPE bottles, PP, and mixed plastics by material and color.</p>\n            <div class=\"product-family-chips\" aria-label=\"Typical materials\">\n              <span>PET bottles</span>\n              <span>HDPE bottles</span>\n              <span>PP plastics</span>\n              <span>Mixed recyclables</span>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"product-family-metrics\" aria-label=\"AI optical sorting highlights\">\n              <div>\n                <dt>0.6-2 t/h</dt>\n                <dd>Throughput range</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>5-10</dt>\n                <dd>Material categories</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>Skid modules</dt>\n                <dd>Faster installation</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\"><a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/ai-optical-sorting\" aria-label=\"View AI optical sorting system details\">View details</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"industrial-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Construction and Bulky Waste Line</p>\n            <h2 id=\"industrial-family-title\">Integrated C&D waste disposal and resource utilization line</h2>\n            <p>The Lion One integrated crushing and screening station combines feeding, crushing, screening, magnetic separation, air separation, and baling equipment.</p>\n            <div class=\"product-engineering-brief\">\n              <ol class=\"product-process-chain\" aria-label=\"Core construction waste process\">\n                <li>Controlled feeding</li>\n                <li>Size reduction</li>\n                <li>Aggregate screening</li>\n                <li>Magnetic separation</li>\n                <li>Air separation</li>\n                <li>Baling</li>\n              </ol>\n              <dl class=\"product-line-specs\" aria-label=\"Construction waste line highlights\">\n                <div>\n                  <dt>Capacity range</dt>\n                  <dd>20-70 t/h</dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>Single-machine footprint</dt>\n                  <dd>35 m<sup>2</sup></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>Adjustable crushing size</dt>\n                  <dd>Hydraulic drive</dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\">\n              <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/construction-waste-recycling-line\" aria-label=\"View construction waste line specification\">View details</a>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN integrated crushing and screening station for construction and decoration waste\">\n          </picture>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"products-inquiry-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ Input</p>\n          <h2 id=\"products-inquiry-title\">Product matching accuracy improves with waste stream, throughput, site limits, and project stage</h2>\n          <p>Share the waste stream, target throughput, site limits, and project stage you are evaluating. WEI LAN can recommend the suitable product line and prepare a more focused configuration review.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-contact-panel compact-contact-panel\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">Request Product Proposal</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/solutions\">Review Solution Paths</a>\n          <p>Sales hotline: +86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"specs\" aria-labelledby=\"specs-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Product Data</p>\n          <h2 id=\"specs-title\">Parameter data gives model comparison a clear technical basis</h2>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-ai\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">Super Optical Sorting</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-ai\">Model range is defined by modular optical sorting configurations</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Mini</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                  <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                  <dt>Power</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                  <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 8 &times; 3 m layout · 3 m clear height</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                  <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET · HDPE · PP · Mixed</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Standard</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                  <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                  <dt>Power</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                  <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 12 &times; 3 m layout · 6 m clear height</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                  <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET colors · HDPE · PP · Mixed · Reject</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                  <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>Power</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 17 &times; 3 m layout · 6 m clear height</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                  <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET colors · HDPE · PP · PE · Mixed · Reject</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-cdw\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">Construction Waste Line</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-cdw\">Lion One integrated station</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Integrated crushing &amp; screening station</p>\n                </div>\n                <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div><dt>MFG</dt><dd>WEI&nbsp;LAN</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>TYPE</dt><dd>MOBILE&nbsp;STATION</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>GRADE</dt><dd>HEAVY&nbsp;DUTY</dd></div>\n                </dl>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">t/h</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Feed size</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">mm</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">m<sup>2</sup> &middot; 11.7 &times; 3 &times; 3.1 m</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Drive</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">full hydraulic</span></dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n              <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">WEI LAN</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>Ningbo, China</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>Integrated Mobile Station</span>\n              </footer>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
